{"tid":705043,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟醜樣嘅人係唔係特別自信心爆棚？","createTime":"2018-06-16T19:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T03:10:44.000Z","uid":151221,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e02879ede3d53c135f8cd19c2f09ff02735ad9","tid":705043,"uid":151221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T19:06:27.000Z","msg":"話說小弟之前工作嘅地方有個好撚豬嘅女同事<br />\n佢係嗰種成日以為全世界都暗戀佢<br />\n但事實上明明就係又毒又成面暗瘡嘅死肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次佢行過黎都r我水吹，係度扮可愛無啦啦喵喵叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁本身都無乜嘢嘅 咪當識多個朋友囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知！！一切都係局黎嘅。<br />\n某一次收左工之後就同成班同事一齊打邊爐<br />\n無意之中閒聊傾起小弟同女友鬧交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係嗰時條八婆就開始有意無意咁成日叫我同女友分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如：<br />\n「拎我女友張相係其他同事面前笑佢柒」<br />\n「不斷同其他人詆毀佢鬧佢港女、豬扒」<br />\n頭嗰一兩次我都以為係我聽錯，所以都無追究<br />\n點知之後竟然變本加厲，直接走過黎同我講不如同女友分手搵過個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當時真係呆撚左，之後忍唔住就鬧鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自此以後就無再講野，咁我以為都告一段落啦。。<br />\n點知！！！佢竟然<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">周圍同其他同事講覺得我鍾意佢！話覺得我比帽我女友，所以想問大家知唔知我女友聯絡方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n好彩嘅係依家都已經無人再理依個傻婆<br />\n但係我聽到真係好撚嬲<br />\n你樣衰我都唔撚介意，見你無朋友可憐你，做你朋友<br />\n點知咁樣俾人玩左一鑊<br />\n究竟依啲人係唔係仲以為自己有資本可以咁樣作惡？<br />\n不如返屋企痾督尿，照下自己個樣先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正評：巴打做得好，依啲人唔鬧唔得<br />\n負評：人地都係想要朋友姐，唔洗做到咁盡"},{"pid":"1bc4d9b36cfba291aa705e6f444e674885d9ec1b","tid":705043,"uid":10277,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T19:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/030801_4571b7917e32e8e1cb224f42e6f28405.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F030801_4571b7917e32e8e1cb224f42e6f28405.png&h=7f61686a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正啦 羨慕樓主 感謝樓主為地球消滅一個肥婆"},{"pid":"ff0a19ed770a26a9b3b532139664bdc7d46eda7d","tid":705043,"uid":151221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bc4d9b36cfba291aa705e6f444e674885d9ec1b","tid":705043,"uid":10277,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T19:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/030801_4571b7917e32e8e1cb224f42e6f28405.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F030801_4571b7917e32e8e1cb224f42e6f28405.png&h=7f61686a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正啦 羨慕樓主 感謝樓主為地球消滅一個肥婆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T19:14:53.000Z","msg":"條肥婆最嘔心嘅地方係成日以為自己好靚女，每日見到佢都係度強調今日自己幾用心打扮，屌打全公司嘅女同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌 有咁多心機不如洗乾淨啲你個頭仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似萬年無洗頭咁&hellip;"},{"pid":"7e7362878ee8f0c171646350302b921105ced980","tid":705043,"uid":161352,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T19:18:53.000Z","msg":"仲有原來肥婆 減肥成功變女神既女仔<br />\n比佢屈我同佢表白 又搞好多動作<br />\n輾轉係女仔fd聽到 真係呆左 重點係啲女仔信曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我諗佢地都係想要自製虛榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde0f90547fbcf2fe17c5d2e7d6aa075f528f302","tid":705043,"uid":151221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e7362878ee8f0c171646350302b921105ced980","tid":705043,"uid":161352,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T19:18:53.000Z","msg":"仲有原來肥婆 減肥成功變女神既女仔<br />\n比佢屈我同佢表白 又搞好多動作<br />\n輾轉係女仔fd聽到 真係呆左 重點係啲女仔信曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=